PN,43701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775394665
OL,3,CSailor taken to hospital after being
OL,4,Crescued in 'complex lifesaving
OL,5,Coperation'
OL,7,FA sailor has been rescued and taken to
OL,8,Fhospital in what has been described as
OL,9,Fa "significant and complex lifesaving
OL,10,Foperation" in Devon.
OL,12,FThe casualty was stuck on a cliff at
OL,13,FBolberry after their boat was wrecked
OL,14,Fby the rocks on the coastline in the
OL,15,Fevening of Thursday 2 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
