FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775394665
OL,3,CSailor taken to hospital after being
OL,4,Crescued in 'complex lifesaving
OL,5,Coperation'
OL,7,FThe sailor was flown to hospital after
OL,8,Freceiving treatment on the cliff top.
OL,9,FThe rescue team has praised a member
OL,10,Fof the public for making a 999 call,
OL,11,Fwithout which the incident "could have
OL,12,Fhad a much different outcome".
OL,14,FFalmouth Coastguard received the call
OL,15,Fjust before 7.30pm, and Kingsbridge
OL,16,FCoastguard Rescue Team and Salcombe
OL,17,FRNLI were sent to the incident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775394665
OL,3,CSailor taken to hospital after being
OL,4,Crescued in 'complex lifesaving
OL,5,Coperation'
OL,7,FUpon arrival, the lifeboat crews
OL,8,Flocated the vessel on the rocks and
OL,9,Fthe wreckage in the water, but could
OL,10,Fnot see the sailor.
OL,12,FFurther responders were deployed to
OL,13,Fassist, including Coastguard Rescue
OL,14,FHelicopter Rescue 924 from Newquay and
OL,15,FYealm Coastguard Rescue team.
OL,17,FThe sailor was heard shouting for help
OL,18,Ffrom the cliffs, where they had
OL,19,Fscrambled nearly 100 metres and were
OL,20,Fstuck in an area not visible to those
OL,21,Fsearching from above.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775394665
OL,3,CSailor taken to hospital after being
OL,4,Crescued in 'complex lifesaving
OL,5,Coperation'
OL,7,FA rope rescue system was set up for a
OL,8,Fmember of the Coastguard to recover
OL,9,Fthem to the safety of the cliff top.
OL,11,FThe team treated the sailor before
OL,12,Fcarrying them on a stretcher over
OL,13,Fsteep terrain to the helicopter which
OL,14,Fflew them to hospital for further care.
OL,16,FSharing photos of the incident online,
OL,17,FKingsbridge Coastguard said: "The
OL,18,Fsuccess of this incident came down to
OL,19,Fseamless teamwork.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775394665
OL,3,CSailor taken to hospital after being
OL,4,Crescued in 'complex lifesaving
OL,5,Coperation'
OL,7,F"The lifeboats perspective, the CRTs
OL,8,Ftechnical rescue capability, and the
OL,9,Fhelicopter crew's medical care and
OL,10,Fevacuation all played vital roles.
OL,12,F"An outstanding effort from everyone
OL,13,Finvolved, and we wish the casualty a
OL,14,Fswift recovery.
OL,16,F"We also want to extend our thanks to
OL,17,Fthe member of the public who made the
OL,18,Fcall, without their 999 call this
OL,19,Fincident could have had a much
OL,20,Fdifferent outcome.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
